# calculator-zig

A simple CLI calculator made in Zig

## Compiling

1. Install Zig
2. Go to the `calculator-zig` directory
3. Run `zig build`
4. An executable will be made in `zig-out/bin`

## Usage

Grab the executable and run using `./calculator` on Linux, and `calculator.exe` on Windows

```
calculator (a: number) (+, -, x, /) (b: number)
```
